Ext.data.JsonP['Arrow_Builder_1.2.62_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Arrow Builder 1.2.62 - 18 September 2015</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46239578\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Arrow Builder 1.2.62 - 18 September 2015</h1>\n    <p>Arrow Builder 1.2.62 is a patch release, addressing high-priority issues from previous releases.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239578_ArrowBuilder1.2.62ReleaseNote-NewFeatures\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New Features</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Create a Swagger Interface as part of the API documentation. For details, see <a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Arrow_Builder_1.2.62_Release_Note-section-src-46239578\">API Builder Docs</a>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Support clearing local logs in the Admin Console.    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239578_ArrowBuilder1.2.62ReleaseNote-FixedIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\"p1 \">    <p>API-1013: Logs in the root directory causing server to reload    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p>API-1015: Server should not restart on certain file/directory changes, such as web/public, web/views/ and package.json    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p>API-1026: Cannot set model fields during a POST in a pre-block on an ArrowDB model    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p>API-1027: Transaction logs still have too much unnecessary data in them    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p>API-1030: Server size was not being applied using appc 5.0.0-30    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p>API-1033: Disable memwatch    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46239578\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Arrow Builder 1.2.62 Release Note"});